title: [Vornavian Coast, Pine Forest]
description: A thick carpet of fallen pine needles covers the ground here, muffling all sounds and creating an uneasy silence.  As the wind subsides, the calls of several nocturnal birds become audible.  Unseen creatures jump from tree to tree overhead, dislodging an occasional branch or pine cone.

A thick carpet of fallen pine needles covers the ground here, muffling all sounds and creating an uneasy silence.  As the wind subsides, the calls of many different kinds of birds become audible.  Squirrels jump from tree to tree overhead, dislodging an occasional branch or pine cone.
